    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "fair enough. so if the whole system is basically designed to let the big players bypass it, does that mean the UN is actually just a failed experiment? like, is it even worth trying to reform it at this point, or is the whole concept of international governance just kind of an outdated dream?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
